<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.5">
<l>kaḷvaṉē ṉāṉēṉ paṭiṟucey tiruppēṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṭavā tiritantē ṉēlum</l>
<l>teḷḷiyē ṉāṉēṉ celkatik kamaintēṉ</l>
<l>cikkeṉat tiruvaruḷ peṟṟēṉ</l>
<l>uḷḷelā murukik kuraltaḻut toḻintē</l>
<l>ṉuṭampelām kaṇṇanīr cōra</l>
<l>naḷḷiru ḷaḷavum pakalunā ṉaḻaippaṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I became a thief; I was committing wrongs.</l>
<l rend="indent">Though I wandered aimlessly at random,</l>
<l>I became wise; I was suited for salvation. I gained divine grace immediately.</l>
<l>[My] whole heart melting, [my] voice faltering, I was speechless.</l>
<l rend="indent">As tears trickled down my body,</l>
<l>The length of the deep of night and [throughout] daylight,</l>
<l rend="indent">I call the name which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
